{"tid":2024056,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《Mad Max Fury Road》5月29日起重返大銀幕","createTime":"2020-05-19T11:25:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T11:50:54.000Z","uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ea0bda2925b64a96df6d83b21d6df89c6c1886ca","tid":2024056,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:25:38.000Z","msg":"【CGS 4K激光巨幕版奧斯卡得獎電影 &quot;Mad Max: Fury Road&quot;《末日先鋒：戰甲飛車》獨家首播】<br />\n<br />\n有些電影注定要在大銀幕觀賞，才能真正享受到光影帶來的視聽震撼。而 &quot;Mad Max: Fury Road&quot;《末日先鋒：戰甲飛車》絕對是一部值得入戲院一看再看的傑作。<br />\n<br />\n配合Premiere Elements的CGS Laser巨幕影廳及THX原音效認證影廳開幕，將全港獨家首播 &quot;Mad Max: Fury Road&quot;《末日先鋒：戰甲飛車》CGS 4K ATMOS巨幕版，影迷可全新欣賞這部跨時代巨獻，全新體驗電影帶來石破天驚的視聽衝擊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此電影於2015年不僅成為國際眾多媒體選出的年度10大電影，更橫掃6項奧斯卡金像獎，包括:「最佳剪接」、「最佳音效剪接」及「最佳混音」等。迅即成為不少影迷的心頭好，絕對稱得上為「新經典」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BePeFh6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBePeFh6.jpg&h=ccf0801e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c04ff7e198f2631a3e7dd5570b755601891412df","tid":2024056,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e2dfd7af99da7cceaa615a2cf3491548f281b8","tid":2024056,"uid":129385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:41:07.000Z","msg":"CGS Laser 查完都唔知有咩勁？<br />\n中國巨幕同大之外+4K?"},{"pid":"00731025304dc5097a25f2ac7c5289d6f9a405e4","tid":2024056,"uid":68033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:50:54.000Z","msg":"已經買左29號飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}